import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IEventProductOrder } from '../event-product-order.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-event-product-order-detail', templateUrl: './event-product-order-detail.component.html', }) export class EventProductOrderDetailComponent implements OnInit { eventProductOrder: IEventProductOrder | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ eventProductOrder }) => { this.eventProductOrder = eventProductOrder; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
